    Author:
    shenli

    The PostalAddressBuilder class represents building postal address information

    PostalAddressBuilder objects are not constant; their values can be changed after they are created. The PostalAddressBuilder object is not thread-safe. To use it concurrently, user must surround each method invocation with external synchronization of the users' choosing.
